title: Boot and Shoe Shipments from Boston for United States
notes:
Data Are Weekly Averages Per Month Using All Weeks With A Majority Of Days In The Month. Source: Computed By NBER From Data Found In The Shoe And Leather Reporter.

This NBER data series m01101 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.

NBER Indicator: m01101
